data.description: This home boasts three bedrooms, one bathroom providing ample space for a growing family, natural light creating a warm and inviting atmosphere, built in shelves adding character and charm, there is a lovely backyard that provides a perfect space for relaxation, gardening, or entertaining guests. spacious enough for an ADU. Attached Garage. Conveniently located near Berkeley’s vibrant areas, Fourth street shops, restaurants, public transportation and freeways. Need some updating. Looking to create your dream home look no further.
